  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "2015-04-16", 
    "text": "Foreclosure Fairness Act of 2015 \n\n Prohibits a court, in the case of any federally related mortgage loan made after enactment of this Act, from entering a deficiency judgment requiring the mortgagor to pay any balance on the mortgage loan after a foreclosure sale of the mortgaged property."
